--- !u!114 &655359756
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 655359754}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 81fd3b94799484510bf9df411fb36fe5, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  items:
  - itemName: Turret
    icon: {fileID: 21300000, guid: f3fac4ec382164bc28dbc5d818d66110, type: 3}
    price: 25
    description: Ever wanted to get rid of those pesky birds? Look no further than
      the Turret! These bad boys run purely on our very good batteries that can last
      just as how long you last in bed!
  - itemName: ScarecrowSiren
    icon: {fileID: 21300000, guid: c48414a8cf8d34df887f5f54312e922c, type: 3}
    price: 75
    description: 'Need to get those birds away from you? Place one of these bad boys
      and it''ll scare them so much they''ll never come back, if they can see them
      that is. We tried it don''t work at nighttime and our customers hate looking
      at it! '
  - itemName: BirdTrap
    icon: {fileID: 21300000, guid: add3a3abdf2e34e9291bd3d8de0d0842, type: 3}
    price: 150
    description: What's better than shooing those birds away? Why trapping them of
      course! Using our scientifically made worms those birds won't be able to resist!
      Our product is so good even our customers get trapped by it
  - itemName: Coyote
    icon: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 5e3eca4ac98e4405494e981edba0ea7a, type: 3}
    price: 200
    description: If you hate the roadrunner, you're gonna love this! This fast coyote
      can reach speeds even faster than the roadrunner, just don't have him near
      people, he's afraid of them
  - itemName: ParkBoots
    icon: {fileID: 21300000, guid: fab25c6d427314f109afc2ecc73b2515, type: 3}
    price: 175
    description: With our special limted edition Park Boots, these shoes will keep
      you to the ground and increase running speed! They need to remain clean every
      day or its effects don't work.
  - itemName: RoboCleaner
    icon: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 2d7b80d7ff63e4182abd98674ddf21fb, type: 3}
    price: 400
    description: Man I hate those birds pooping everywhere, so look no further to
      the RoboCleaner! These bots will take care of the bird poop! Just make sure
      you empty out the bots storage!
  - itemName: Teacher
    icon: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 3af3c54eafea44fe5b1ad90f8dc43c9d, type: 3}
    price: 500
    description: 'If you want to get those naughty teenagers, our teachers will make
      sure those teenagers won''t come back by teenagers worst fear: Small Talk.
      Small talk ain''t easy so they want some money each time or they''ll just quit
      on the spot'
  - itemName: Battery
    icon: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 26815fcc5b1bb4cf098c15a477ad6e67, type: 3}
    price: 100
    description: Are those Turrets of yours running out of battery quickly? Get the
      Battery expansion pack, place these down and they will remotely charge those
      Turrets! But keep them away from the open as those birds as we made them edible
      so we can sell them to children without it being a choking hazard!
