MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 1829931912}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 134fcf7312c6047d7a5edba3d3d65118, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: '::'
  gameOverPanel: {fileID: 411317823}
  pausePanel: {fileID: 213175183}
  pauseCanvasGroup: {fileID: 213175185}
  tipText: {fileID: 876091687}
  pauseTips:
  - text: Did you know...this game was based off the park Montifore Square
  - text: 'The coyote battlecard was based off The RoadRunner Show '
  - text: The main leader of our company FlyHardFools, 21Hugues runs a channel called
      21Hugues
  - text: Bloodwings was banned from Flock Therapy after 3 minutes.
  - text: "Aero once tried to \u201Csave the sky\u201D from a cloud. The cloud won."
  - text: Normal birds still argue about who gets the best branch.
  - text: "Roadrunners don\u2019t walk anywhere. Even in cutscenes."
  - text: Teacher birds give homework. Even in combat. Yes, really.
  - text: When teen birds discovered sarcasm, they immediately abused it.
  - text: The golden bird refuses to explain its powers. It just glows and leaves.
  - text: "Bloodwings say they\u2019re \u201Cjust misunderstood.\u201D They are not."
  - text: Aero's cape gets stuck in doors constantly.
  - text: Birds believe sprinting solves emotional problems.
  - text: Roadrunners have never been seen standing still in lore.
  - text: "Teacher birds can win arguments by saying \u201CI'm going to tell your
      parents\u2026\u201D"
  - text: "Teen birds think flying is \u201Cuncool unless it\u2019s dramatic.\u201D"
  - text: Golden bird once blinked and caused the apocalypse
  - text: Bloodwings blink in lowercase anger.
  - text: "Aero's mask is purely aesthetic\u2026 it just insists otherwise."
  - text: Normal birds form committees for everything, including flying direction.
  - text: Roadrunners consider walking a mythical slow ritual.
  - text: Teacher birds secretly grade other birds mid-fight.
  - text: The sky itself has filed complaints about the birds.
  itemShopPanel: {fileID: 396846193}
  startButton: {fileID: 343758987}
  gameOverCanvasGroup: {fileID: 411317827}
